{
  "title": "Robust Peppery Australian Papelon Stew",
  "description": "A hearty and flavorful pescatarian stew featuring papelon, perfect for a family dinner. This kid-friendly dish is made with namul-blanch-seasoned ingredients and cooked to perfection in a Dutch oven.",
  "cuisine": "Australian",
